      "content": "fair enough. but i noticed u mentioned the \"climate goals\" earlier. i feel like a lot of times when people talk about these things, they act like there's no other choice but to ditch coal because of the environment. do u think there's actually a valid argument for keeping the coal credits as they are, or is that just outdated thinking?",
